===Interjection===
'''dude''' 
#(''slang'') Be careful!
#: '' '''Dude'''!  You're going to hit that car.''
#(''slang'') You should have been more careful!  Often spoken with an extended "u" sound imitative of the slurred speach and delayed reaction time of a long-term user of marijuana.  Popularized by the comedian Tommy Chong.
#: '' '''.......Duuuude'''!  You almost went off that cliff.''


